Aclaraciones sobre funciones y algo mas del codigo

System.getProperty("user.dir") me da la ruta donde estoy parado

HttpHandler staticHandler = new HttpHandler();
Crea un HttpHandler que maneja requests a un recurso estatico que esta en un determinado directorio.

Endpoints:The endpoint is a connection point where HTML files or active server pages are exposed. 
Endpoints provide information needed to address a Web service endpoint. 
The endpoint provides a reference or specification that is used to define a group or family of message 
addressing properties and give end-to-end message characteristics, 
such as references for the source and destination of endpoints, 
and the identity of messages to allow for uniform addressing of "independent" messages. 
The endpoint can be a PC, PDA, or point-of-sale terminal.

